Dancing with my brides has been the most special moment for me❤️❤️❤️#notwithoutmybrides .
.

.
I met Sayali 4 years ago, while I was designing performances at her best friends wedding! Couple of years later and lots of performances together at most of her friends weddings, we collaborated again at her own wedding 2 years ago!  With that heart of gold and her charming personality filled with warmth and kindness, she is one of the most beautiful brides inside out that I have ever worked with! .
.

.
.
.

We hope you enjoy it as much as we did creating it❤️
To watch her Sangeet performance on “chalka” click on the link in bio and subscribe to the you tube channel.
